{
  "description": "A close-up, overhead shot of a tulip flower in full bloom. The flower is a soft, muted pink with darker pink and purple hues towards the base of its petals, creating a subtle gradient. The petals are slightly curled and have delicate veins running through them. The stamen and pistil are visible in the center, with dark purple anthers topped with yellow pollen. The background is a solid, deep black, which emphasizes the flower's form and color. The focus is sharp on the petals and reproductive parts, with a slight falloff towards the edges, contributing to a sense of depth.",
